snippet.textDisplay:
Pata nahi ye kaunse Kashmiri hai jo har video mein  dikh jaate hai, khaskhar Pakistani video mein, mein jaanta hoon ye asli Kashmiri nahi hai, ye woh log hai,jo Hurriyat ko follow karte hai yaa phir Pakistan ki dashtgardi ko support karte hai, 
Ye log kehte hai, ki Kashmir mein Bada zulm ho raha hai, ye log kehte hai, ki Kashmir mein hazaaron log marte hai, 
Mein sawaal karta hoon? 
en sabke liye kaun kasoorwaar hai, Hindustan yaa Pakistan,jawaab hai Pakistan. 
Agar itne saal se pakistan ki taraf se dashtgardi naa hoti, toh shayad kashmiryon pe zulm naa hote, agar itne saal se Pakistan ki taraf se dashtgardi naa hoti, toh shayad kashmiri naa marte hai, 
Kuch log aise jinhein lagta hai, ki Kashmir mein zulm hote hai, ek baar Kashmir chale kyun nahi jaate, dekhlo naa ki wahan pe Kashmiriyon pe zulm ho rahe hai yaa nahi, mein gaya hoon Kashmir mein,koi zulm nahi hote kahmiriyon pe, mein invitation deta hoon, un logon ko jo yeh kehte hai ki Kashmiriyon pe zulm hote hai, ek baar aao kashmir  mein dekho kashmiriyon pe zulm ho rahe hai yaa nahi. 
Ye jo har video aake kehte ho naa ki Kashmir mein zulm ho rahe,
Behtar yahin hoga, ki Kashmir mein aake dekhlo,ki kashmiryon pe zulm ho rahe hai ki nahi, 
Aur last mein tumhaare jaise log ko hum jawaab dete rahenge, yaad rakhna chahiye Hindustan ki awaam ho, chahiye Kashmir ki awaam ho, hum sab tumhein jawaab denge
